BetterLC - Unlock Company Tags on LeetCode for Free

Enhance your LeetCode experience with BetterLC! Unlock company tags effortlessly by simply opening any LeetCode problem and hovering over the embedded BetterLC icon. Gain insights into which companies ask specific problems, helping you prepare more effectively for interviews.

To support the development and maintenance of the extension, occasional ads may pop under in the background. These ads are non-intrusive and won't disturb your user experience.

Empower your preparation with BetterLC!
